<a name="details" id="details"></a><h2 id="header-details" class="groupheader">Detailed Description</h2>
<div class="textblock"><p>Core type definitions and fixed-width aliases. </p>
<p>Ensures strict standard compliance where possible and provides standardized, short-hand type aliases for fixed-width integers and floats. </p>

<p class="definition">Definition in file <a class="el" href="base__types_8h_source.html">base_types.h</a>.</p>
